## 4. EXEMPLOS DE REGRAS YAML PARA GUARDS DE @LOCKS E SSOT

### 4.1 Guard de @LOCK (bloqueio reativo)

```yaml
# .nc/hooks/lockguard.yaml
hooks:
  - event: tool_called
    matcher:
      tool_type: Edit|Write|MultiEdit|Delete
      file_pattern: "**/server.py|**/sub_server.py|**/NCNAMFR001*"
    script: hooks/lockguard.py
    action: block
    priority: 1000  # alta prioridade
    metadata:
      lock_type: atomic
      override_env: "NC_ATOMIC_OVERRIDE"
```

### 4.2 Guard de SSOT (atualizao automtica)

```yaml
# .nc/hooks/ssotguard.yaml
hooks:
  - event: file_written
    matcher:
      file_pattern: "**/NCLBE*.mdc|**/NCDS*.yaml|**/NCTOOLFR*.py"
    script: hooks/ssotupdate.py
    action: log
    priority: 500
    metadata:
      ssot_table: "NCNAMFR001namingregistry.yaml"
      auto_update: true
```

### 4.3 Guard de Naming Convention (NC*)

```yaml
# .nc/hooks/namingguard.yaml
hooks:
  - event: file_written
    matcher:
      file_pattern: "**/*.py|**/*.yaml|**/*.md"
    script: hooks/namingvalidator.py
    action: warn
    priority: 300
    metadata:
      pattern: "^NC[A-Z]{3,5}[A-Z]{2}[0-9]{3}.*"
      error_message: "Nome de arquivo no segue conveno NC*"
```

